I saw a picture of a dark knight in armor and I must say I agree with you on the graphics - they are absolutely AWESOME. Are there not many people in the world? Or did you mean the world felt empty in a different way?<br>
Combat - I have read this was practically the same as EQ's. You press a button to auto attack, and then you press some other buttons to do some skills, such as EQ's kick and taunt buttons. I am assuming for the most part this is how it is set up anyhow.<br>
The music I heard on the live feed was so great. This is one aspect of EQ that you dont really get. Very little music in EQ, anyone noticed?<br>
All in all, if I do not get this for Christmas I will surely buy it soon after. Nakath - are you on Bismarck with Firiona Reborn?<br>
